title: Big Brother: Late & Live
overview: AJ Odudu, Will Best and a host of celebs look back at all the drama from the iconic Big Brother house with unseen exclusive extra footage along with the latest gossip.Join AJ and Will once they've finished with the main show as they present all the hot-off-the-press news and gossip from the housemates' week in the house and get a scoop on Friday when they have an exclusive interview with the evicted housemate.Â
